  "text": "The establishment of an INV requires the development of international contacts but our results indicated that IE operating INV developed even more international connections than NE operating INV. This finding is aligned with research by [CITATION_1] , which concluded that immigrant-founded firms are more likely to report that they have a strategic relationship with a foreign firm.",
